%N A394814 Number of directed self-avoiding cycles of length 2*n in a cubic lattice, reduced for symmetry (with rotations and reflections not counted as distinct).
%e A394814 a(4) = 13 (with uppercase letters denoting positive direction steps in XYZ coordinates and lowercase denoting negative steps): 9 symmetric cases counting 1 each: XXXYxxxy, XXYYxxyy, XXYYxyxy, XXYxZyxz, XXYZxxyz, XXYZxxzy, XXYZyxxz, XYXZxyxz, XYZyxYzy, plus 2 nonsymmetric cases counting 2 each: XXYZxyxz, XXYZxzxy.
%Y A394814 Cf. A394959 (2-dimensional), A394796 (undirected), A394340 (directed paths), A001409 (undirected, all orientations), A001413 (all walks, all orientations).
%K A394814 nonn,more,walk,new
